description:
PmEventService:  Table containing performance management (PM) event service configuration and status for each cell.

dateTime: Timestamp indicating when the data was recorded.
Area_Name: Name of the geographic area where the cell is located (e.g., NR_Balikpapan).
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell site.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  An arbitrary identifier (likely redundant).
vsDataType: Type of data; in this case, performance management event service data.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format used (Ericsson-specific).
PmEventService.ueTraceFileSize: Size of a single UE trace file (bytes).
PmEventService.totalCellTraceStorageSize: Total storage size allocated for cell traces (bytes).
PmEventService.cellTraceHighPrioReserve: Reserved storage for high-priority cell traces (bytes).
PmEventService.cellTraceFileSize: Size of a single cell trace file (bytes).
PmEventService.ueTraceSyncF1AndE1WithX2: Boolean indicating whether UE trace synchronization between F1, E1, and X2 interfaces is enabled.
PmEventService.streamStatusPmCellTrace: Status of the cell trace stream.
PmEventService.totalEventStorageSize: Total storage size allocated for events (bytes).
PmEventService.totalUeTraceStorageSize: Total storage size allocated for UE traces (bytes).
PmEventService.streamPortPmUeTrace: Port number used for the UE trace stream.
PmEventService.cellTracePeriodicReport: Boolean indicating whether periodic cell trace reports are enabled.
PmEventService.streamStatusNotification: Boolean indicating the status of stream notifications.
PmEventService.pmEventServiceId: Unique identifier for the PM event service instance.
PmEventService.streamStatusPmUeTrace: Status of the UE trace stream.
